E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('806','8','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">任何企业的成功绝非偶然，他们都是经过了奋斗路上的披荆斩棘，历经风风雨雨才有今天的成就。自古以来，无论是成功的个人还是卓越的团队，没有谁天生就是胜利者，</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\\\\\">没有谁能够一帆风顺。成功的背后是多少次失败的磨砺，光环的背后是多少次绝望的呐喊。</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\\\\\">作为佛山知名的</span></span><a href=\\\\\"http://www.hudsonhome.cn/xwzx/qyxw/2014-09-14/507.html\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: #0000ff\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\"16\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\\\\\">一线瓷砖品牌</span></span></span></a><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\\\\\">，哈德逊瓷砖历尽艰辛，在陶瓷行业电商之路上不畏艰难，敢于做行业的领头羊，带动了陶瓷行业走上发展电商之路。宝剑锋从磨砺出，哈德逊瓷砖克服重重困境，最终成为赢者。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"广东瓷砖二线品牌.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"550\\\\\" height=\\\\\"425\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2015-01-10/7813e50b634b496e30764d7d3a41f4fa.jpg\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\\\\\">哈德逊瓷砖隶属于</span><span class=\\\\\"15\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">佛山市哈德逊经贸有限公司</span><span class=\\\\\"15\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">旗下的一个瓷砖品牌。而</span><span class=\\\\\"15\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">佛山市哈德逊经贸有限公司</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体